ing the work?\n+\n+The UI should support both broad scanning and exact drill-down. A reviewer\n+should be able to start at the PR overview, jump into a highlighted turn, expand\n+the relevant tool call or assistant claim, then return to the overview without\n+losing context.\n+\n+Raw transcript records should remain available, but they should be treated as an\n+evidence drawer, not the primary browsing mode.\n \n ## Ranking And Highlighting\n \n The page should rank or highlight likely relevant turns. Relevance is a product\n*** End Patch\n","source_record":{"timestamp":"2026-05-24T14:22:42.664Z","type":"response_item","payload":{"type":"custom_tool_call","status":"completed","call_id":"[REDACTED:entropy]","name":"apply_patch"}}}